but in just a different place.

41:05.333 --> 41:06.958
There's not only one or two.

41:07.042 --> 41:09.875
There are many,
many different races.

41:10.042 --> 41:14.333
And coming in contact
with other races or beings

41:14.458 --> 41:17.292
is coming in the next epoch.

41:19.083 --> 41:21.333
TZADOK:
The purpose of the teachings

41:21.417 --> 41:23.667
of the mystical traditions

41:23.750 --> 41:28.333
is to provide light
and redirection back

41:28.458 --> 41:31.167
to communion
with the higher domains.

41:31.250 --> 41:33.958
We are not alone

41:34.042 --> 41:38.750
as intelligent beings
upon our own Earth.

41:39.708 --> 41:43.667
NARRATOR: Is humanity
rapidly approaching the day

41:43.833 --> 41:46.583
when the secrets
of Inner Earth will be revealed?

41:46.708 --> 41:49.042
Have we been sharing the planet

41:49.208 --> 41:51.625
with other
intelligent life-forms

41:51.708 --> 41:53.333
for thousands of years?

